<plot>The racism skinhead gang White Rage has one mission: To defend and protect Denmark from new-coming strangers of immigration. Under a nightly battle against an immigration gang, the leader Stigs, gets temporarily deadly injured, and fells into coma. After he gets into a Hospital, his younger brother Jens considers himself as the new gang leader. Without any notice of the other gang members, Jens makes a secret deal with the immigration gang, about piece and no weapons. But when Jens realises that another member of the gang Lars, also seeks the leader position, he is forced to choose between the two gangs.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?429390</url></doc>
